#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:1
msgid "如何运行策略优化"
msgstr "Comment exécuter l'optimisation de la stratégie"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:3
msgid "入口与常用 kwargs"
msgstr "Point d'entrée et kwargs communs"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:5
msgid ""
"使用 **qt.run(op, mode=2, ...)** 运行策略优化。常用参数包括 "
"**opti_method**、**opti_sample_count**、**opti_output_count** 等。"
msgstr ""
"Exécutez l'optimisation de la stratégie avec **``qt.run(op, mode=2, "
"...)``**. Common arguments include **``opti_method``**, "
"**``opti_sample_count``**, **``opti_output_count``** et d'autres."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:7
msgid "优化算法完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr ""
"Liste complète des algorithmes d'optimisation (avec de brèves explications)"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:9
msgid "以下为 **opti_method** 常见可选值及适用场景，与 qteasy 2.0 API 一致为准。"
msgstr ""
"Voici les valeurs **``opti_method``** courantes et les cas d'utilisation "
"typiques ; reportez-vous à l'API qteasy 2.0 comme source de vérité."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "算法名"
msgstr "Algorithme"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Signification"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "适用场景"
msgstr "Cas d'utilisation typique"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "grid"
msgstr "grid"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "网格搜索"
msgstr "Recherche par grille"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数少、离散空间，穷举或粗网格。"
msgstr ""
"Peu de paramètres, espace discret ; recherche de grille exhaustive ou "
"grossière."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "montecarlo"
msgstr "montecarlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "蒙特卡洛随机采样"
msgstr "Échantillonnage aléatoire de Monte Carlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数较多时随机抽样评估。"
msgstr "Échantillonnage aléatoire lorsqu'il existe de nombreux paramètres."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "GA"
msgstr "GA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "遗传算法"
msgstr "Algorithme génétique"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中高维、连续/离散混合。"
msgstr "Dimensions moyennes à élevées ; espaces mixtes continus/discrets."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "SA"
msgstr "SA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "模拟退火"
msgstr "Recuit simulé"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中维、易陷入局部最优时。"
msgstr ""
"Dimensions moyennes ; utile lorsque les optima locaux sont une "
"préoccupation."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "PSO"
msgstr "PSO"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "粒子群优化"
msgstr "Optimisation des essaims de particules"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "连续空间、多峰。"
msgstr "Espace continu avec plusieurs sommets."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "bayesian"
msgstr "bayesian"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "贝叶斯优化"
msgstr "Optimisation bayésienne"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "样本昂贵、需少步数寻优。"
msgstr "Évaluations coûteuses ; besoin de bons résultats en quelques étapes."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:20
msgid "优化运行参数完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr ""
"Liste complète des paramètres d'exécution d'optimisation (avec de brèves "
"explications)"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数名"
msgstr "Nom du paramètre"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "类型/可选值"
msgstr "Type / Valeurs"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_method"
msgstr "opti_method"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "str"
msgstr "str"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "优化算法：grid、montecarlo、GA、SA、PSO、bayesian 等。"
msgstr ""
"Algorithme d'optimisation : ``grid``, ``montecarlo``, ``GA``, ``SA``, "
"``PSO``, ``bayesian``, etc."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_sample_count"
msgstr "opti_sample_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "int"
msgstr "int"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "采样/迭代次数（如蒙特卡洛样本数、遗传代数等）。"
msgstr ""
"Nombre d'échantillons/itérations (par exemple, échantillons de Monte Carlo "
"ou générations GA)."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_output_count"
msgstr "opti_output_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "保留的最优结果数量（Top-K）。"
msgstr "Nombre de meilleurs résultats à conserver (Top-K)."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "目标函数相关"
msgstr "Fonction objectif"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "—"
msgstr "—"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "如优化目标为夏普、回撤等，以配置或 API 为准。"
msgstr ""
"Par exemple, ratio de Sharpe ou drawdown ; voir la documentation de "
"configuration ou d'API."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "约束相关"
msgstr "Contraintes"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "若有约束（如最大回撤上限），以配置为准。"
msgstr ""
"Si des contraintes s'appliquent (par exemple, limite de prélèvement "
"maximale), voir la configuration."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:30
msgid "回测区间、asset_pool 等与 mode=1 相同的参数在 mode=2 时同样生效。"
msgstr ""
"Plage de dates de backtest, ``asset_pool``, and other arguments shared with "
"``mode=1`` also apply in ``mode=2``."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:32
msgid "参数空间"
msgstr "Espace des paramètres"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:34
msgid ""
"策略的 **Parameter** 及 **par_range** 定义优化时的搜索空间；框架按 opti_method 在该空间内采样或搜索。"
msgstr ""
"Le **``Parameter``** objects and **``par_range``** define the search space; "
"the framework samples or searches within it according to ``opti_method`` de "
"la stratégie."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:36
msgid "最小可运行示例"
msgstr "Exemple d'exécution minimal"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:47
msgid "配置要点"
msgstr "Points forts de la configuration"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:49
msgid "**回测区间、资产池**：与 mode=1 一致，决定每次参数评估的回测环境。"
msgstr ""
"**Plage de backtest et pool d'actifs** : Identique à ``mode=1`` ; ils "
"définissent l'environnement de backtest pour chaque évaluation de paramètre."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:50
msgid "**目标函数**：决定“更优”的定义（如夏普最大化、回撤最小化），影响排序与最终选取。"
msgstr ""
"**Fonction objectif** : définit ce que « mieux » signifie (par exemple, "
"maximiser Sharpe ou minimiser le retrait) et affecte le classement et la "
"sélection finale."
